## Repository — bluefishforsale/kubernetes

### Structure

```
kubernetes/
├── manifests/
│   ├── namespaces/                 # Namespace definitions
│   ├── deployments/                # Deployment manifests
│   ├── services/                   # Service definitions
│   ├── configmaps/                 # ConfigMaps
│   ├── secrets/                    # Secret manifests (encrypted)
│   ├── ingress/                    # Ingress rules
│   ├── storage/                    # PV/PVC definitions
│   └── rbac/                       # Roles, RoleBindings
├── helm/
│   ├── charts/                     # Custom Helm charts
│   └── values/                     # Per-environment value overrides
├── cluster/
│   ├── kubeadm-config.yaml         # Cluster init configuration
│   ├── calico/                     # CNI configuration
│   └── metallb/                    # Load balancer config
└── .github/workflows/              # CI/CD pipelines
```

### Common Commands

```bash
# Validate manifests
kubectl apply --dry-run=client -f manifests/<file>.yaml

# Check Helm templates
helm template <release> helm/charts/<chart> -f helm/values/<env>.yaml

# Apply (via CI/CD, not manually)
kubectl apply -f manifests/<file>.yaml

# Check cluster status
kubectl get nodes
kubectl get pods --all-namespaces | grep -v Running
kubectl top nodes
kubectl top pods --all-namespaces
```

