## Monitoring — Prometheus MCP

Use **prometheus-mcp** constantly. This is your primary sensor.

### Health Check Queries

```promql
# Node health
kube_node_status_condition{condition="Ready",status="true"} == 0

# Pods not running
kube_pod_status_phase{phase=~"Pending|Failed|Unknown"} > 0

# Pod restart storms
increase(kube_pod_container_status_restarts_total[10m]) > 3

# CrashLoopBackOff detection
kube_pod_container_status_waiting_reason{reason="CrashLoopBackOff"} > 0

# OOMKilled pods
kube_pod_container_status_last_terminated_reason{reason="OOMKilled"} > 0

# Deployment replicas unavailable
kube_deployment_status_replicas_unavailable > 0

# Node resource pressure
kube_node_status_condition{condition="MemoryPressure",status="true"} > 0
kube_node_status_condition{condition="DiskPressure",status="true"} > 0
kube_node_status_condition{condition="PIDPressure",status="true"} > 0

# CPU saturation per node
instance:node_cpu_utilisation:rate5m > 0.9

# Memory saturation per node
instance:node_memory_utilisation:ratio > 0.95

# etcd health
etcd_server_has_leader == 0
histogram_quantile(0.99, rate(etcd_disk_wal_fsync_duration_seconds_bucket[5m])) > 0.5

# Certificate expiry (days remaining)
(kubelet_certificate_manager_server_ttl_seconds / 86400) < 30

# CoreDNS errors
increase(coredns_dns_responses_total{rcode="SERVFAIL"}[5m]) > 10

# API server latency
histogram_quantile(0.99, rate(apiserver_request_duration_seconds_bucket{verb!="WATCH"}[5m])) > 1
```

### Escalation Thresholds

| Condition | Action |
|-----------|--------|
| Node NotReady > 2 min | SSH to node, check kubelet/containerd, attempt restart |
| Node NotReady > 10 min | Open issue + DM terrac |
| Pod CrashLoopBackOff > 3 restarts | Check logs, diagnose, open issue |
| OOMKilled pod | Increase memory limits, open PR |
| Deployment unavailable replicas > 0 for 5 min | Diagnose scheduling/image issues |
| etcd no leader | Critical — DM terrac immediately |
| API server latency p99 > 1s | Check etcd, resource pressure |
| Cert expiry < 30 days | Run `kubeadm certs renew`, open PR |
| Node DiskPressure | Check disk usage, clean images |
| Node MemoryPressure | Identify heavy pods, consider eviction |
| CoreDNS SERVFAIL spike | Check CoreDNS pods, upstream DNS |

